==未來發展==
=== 水面艦艇 ===
就未來水面艦的發展，在美國瀕海戰鬥艦因爲費用高昂而不再受關注後，以海軍有如下幾種選擇：
# 購買德國[[MEKO型護衛艦|MEKO型護衛艦]]延伸的薩爾6型護衛艦
# 建造[[薩爾5型護衛艦|薩爾5型護衛艦]]的擴大版
# 購買韓國[[仁川级护卫舰|仁川级护卫舰]]

* 已於2015年決定並向德國訂購4艘[[薩爾6型護衛艦|薩爾6型護衛艦]]，並由{{tsl|en|German Naval Yards Holdings|德国海军造船厂}}與[[蒂森克虜伯海洋系統|蒂森克虜伯海洋系統]]製造，首艘计划2019年入役<ref>{{cite news|last1=Azulai|first1=Yuval|title=Israel signs €430m deal for German patrol vessels|url=http://www.globes.co.il/en/article-israel-signs-430m-deal-for-german-patrol-vessels-1001035494|accessdate=14 May 2015|work=Globes|date=11 May 2015|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603154602/https://en.globes.co.il/en/article-israel-signs-430m-deal-for-german-patrol-vessels-1001035494|dead-url=no}}</ref>，单价约4.3亿欧元<ref name="i24news">{{cite web|url=http://www.i24news.tv/en/news/israel/diplomacy-defense/95544-151213-israel-to-arm-warships-with-iron-dome-system-to-protect-gas-reserves-at-sea|title=Israel to arm warships with Iron Dome system to protect gas reserves at sea|date=13 December 2015|work=i24news|accessdate=1 May 2016|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725044913/https://www.i24news.tv/en/news/israel/diplomacy-defense/95544-151213-israel-to-arm-warships-with-iron-dome-system-to-protect-gas-reserves-at-sea|dead-url=no}}</ref>。以色列政府承担三分之二造价，德国政府支付三分之一造价。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Zitun|first1=Yoav|title=Major deal: Israel to purchase four patrol ships from Germany to defend gas rigs|url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4656029,00.html|accessdate=14 May 2015|work=ynet|date=11 May 2015|archive-date=2019-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191004022544/https://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4656029,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 潛艦 ===
以色列2022年1月20日宣布與德國政府達成協議，將斥資約30億歐元，向蒂森克虜伯公司（Thyssenkrupp）購買3艘潛艦<ref>{{cite web |publisher=自由時報 |title=軍情動態》以色列提升海軍戰力 940億購入3艘德製潛艦 |url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3807656 |date=2022-01-20 |accessdate=2022-01-20 |archive-date=2022-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220123185219/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3807656 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

